<item>
            <title>[HIVE-23339] SBA does not check permissions for DB location specified in Create or Alter database query</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-23339</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With doAs=true and StorageBasedAuthorization provider, create database with specific location succeeds even if user doesn&apos;t have access to that path.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
  hadoop fs -ls -d /tmp/cannot_write
 drwx------ - hive hadoop 0 2020-04-01 22:53 /tmp/cannot_write

create a database under /tmp/cannot_write. We would expect it to fail, but is actually created successfully with &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hive&quot;&lt;/span&gt; as the owner:

rtrivedi@bdp01:~&amp;gt; beeline -e &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;create database rtrivedi_1 location &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/tmp/cannot_write/rtrivedi_1&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
 INFO : OK
 No rows affected (0.116 seconds)
hive@hpchdd2e:~&amp;gt; hadoop fs -ls /tmp/cannot_write
 Found 1 items
 drwx------ - hive hadoop 0 2020-04-01 23:05 /tmp/cannot_write/rtrivedi_1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
